VICTORIA, Seychelles, April 10, 2018/APO Group/ --
                                                
                        Following the re-election of Hungarian Prime Minister, H.E. Mr. Viktor Orban, President Danny Faure has extend his congratulations following his and the Fidesz party's victory.  
                            I look forward to working with you to further enhance the excellent relationship between our two countries for the benefit of our peoples
                        



In his message, President Faure said that under the leadership of Prime Minister Orban Hungary will continue on its path towards even greater economic prosperity and development for its people. 

"I look forward to working with you to further enhance the excellent relationship between our two countries for the benefit of our peoples," said President Faure.